Class Scan

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortify.pub.issueparsing.Scan
  • public class Scan
extends java.lang.Object
    The scan object contains the general information for the scan, as well as the instance ids of the issues that were included

This is parser specific attribute that helps SSC to understand if data provided by new version of the parser is compatible with data provided by previous versions of the parser. The meaning of this attribute is different that meaning of engine version attribute.
